      <description>&lt;aside class=&#34;callout callout--note&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;callout__body&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document does not describe a hypothetical stress case.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;PlainSight Lab works in domains where failure is already occurring, correction is already too costly, and abstraction itself becomes a form of moral evasion.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Child trafficking is not treated as an extreme example.&#xA;It is treated as a real, ongoing system failure that existing technical, institutional, and governance models have proven unable to contain.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/aside&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;mission&#34;&gt;Mission&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;PlainSight Lab exists to build systems that remain correct under conditions where failure is morally unacceptable and correction is structurally constrained.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
