    <item>
      <title>Truth &amp; Governance Evolution</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/docs/truth-governance-evolution/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/truth-governance-evolution/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the intended lifecycle of truth, governance, and legitimacy across PlainSight Lab and its derivative entities. It exists to align decision-making during early construction, prevent structural drift, and ensure that expansion occurs only when correction costs are safely bounded.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This framework is not a growth roadmap. It is a legitimacy and survivability model.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;phase-1--founder-led-truth-anchoring-current&#34;&gt;Phase 1 — Founder-Led Truth Anchoring (Current)&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Single protocol. Single implementation. Single governance authority.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This phase is correct and necessary. It is not a compromise.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
